stimulusitem1: You will be shown arithmetic problems to solve.   You have a max of 5 seconds for each problem.  All problems have solutions ranging from 0-9.    A response dial with buttons 0-9 will appear on the screen. Press the button that corresponds to the solution.    If you make a mistake, a red X is presented to remind you to be more careful.    Press CONTINUE to start a demo trial.
Get ready.  For each round, you will have 3 minutes to solve as many problems as you can.      Press START to start the round.
